6.00	Shaft_(television)	Shaft (TV series)	Shaft is a series of TV movies that aired along with Hawkins during 1973-74 television season on The New CBS Tuesday Night Movies. The series was based on three films beginning with Shaft (released in 1971), and starring Richard Roundtree as private detective John Shaft.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/aa/Richard_Roundtree_Ed_Barth_Shaft_%28television_version%29_1973.JPG/220px-Richard_Roundtree_Ed_Barth_Shaft_%28television_version%29_1973.JPG
